import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { Nav, NavDropdown,DropdownButton  } from 'react-bootstrap';
import '../styles/CategoryMenu.css';

class CatagoryMenu extends Component {

	render() {
		return (
			<Nav justify variant="tabs" defaultActiveKey="/home" as="ul">
				<Nav.Item as="li">
					<Nav.Link href="/home">Clothing</Nav.Link>

				</Nav.Item>
				<Nav.Item as="li">
					<Nav.Link eventKey="link-1">Sportwear</Nav.Link>
				</Nav.Item>
				<Nav.Item as="li">
					<Nav.Link eventKey="link-2">Outwear</Nav.Link>
				</Nav.Item>
				<Nav.Item as="li">
					<Nav.Link eventKey="link-3">Bags</Nav.Link>
				</Nav.Item>
				<Nav.Item as="li">
					<Nav.Link eventKey="link-4">Shose</Nav.Link>
				</Nav.Item>
				<Nav.Item as="li">
					<Nav.Link eventKey="link-5">Beauty</Nav.Link>
				</Nav.Item>
				<Nav.Item as="li">
					<Nav.Link eventKey="link-6">Accessories</Nav.Link>
				</Nav.Item>

				<DropdownButton bsStyle="default" title="No caret" noCaret id="dropdown-no-caret">
					<MenuItem eventKey="1">Action</MenuItem>
					<MenuItem eventKey="2">Another action</MenuItem>
					<MenuItem eventKey="3">Something else here</MenuItem>
					<MenuItem divider />
					<MenuItem eventKey="4">Separated link</MenuItem>
				</DropdownButton>
			</Nav>
		);
	}
}

export default CatagoryMenu;
